-- Sarkozy Says Mediapart Report on Qaddafi Funding Is ‘An Infamy’
-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i
-- 2012-04-29T14:42:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/sarkozy-says-mediapart-report-on-qaddafi-funding-is-an-infamy-.html
French President  Nicolas Sarkozy 
denied a report that his 2007 presidential campaign allegedly
received funding from former Libyan leader Muammar Qaddafi.  “It’s an infamy, it’s a set-up,” Sarkozy said today in an
 interview  on Canal Plus television, speaking of the report on
the  Mediapart  website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini in Paris at 
